这条古道是由两位登山爱好者成立于2007年，以色列犹太企业家莫茲·艾諾在以色列建立了旅馆和宾馆<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/travel/feature/20130517-walking-with-jesus-in-the-galilee |title=Walking with Jesus in the Galilee |publisher=BBC |date= |accessdate=2013-05-22 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324181248/http://www.bbc.com/travel/feature/20130517-walking-with-jesus-in-the-galilee |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而大卫·兰迪斯是一位美国基督徒登山专家 hiking.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801555.htm |title=CNS STORY: In northern Israel, walking from village to village, like Jesus |publisher=Catholicnews.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20080408212330/http://www.catholicnews.com/data/stories/cns/0801555.htm |archivedate=2008-04-08 }}</ref>。步道目前由志愿者管理，是一个非盈利项目<ref>{{cite web |last=Vered |first=Ronit |url=http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/956795.html |title=Five Stops in the Galilee - Haaretz Daily Newspaper | Israel News |publisher=Haaretz.com |date=2011-09-09 |accessdate=2012-02-03 |archive-date=2010-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326041453/http://www.haaretz.com/hasen/spages/956795.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

耶稣步道对所有远足和露营者免费开放，沿路岩石上设置白色，橙色和白色三色标志。

耶稣步道的圣经依据出自[[马太福音|马太福音]]。[[耶稣|耶稣]]开始公开传道，离开家乡[[拿撒勒|拿撒勒]]，以加利利海边的迦百农为基地（“自己的城市”）。 

